          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1715617573279-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and dice half your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining shallot </strong>finely</p><p>Add the <strong>diced shallot</strong> to a large bowl with your <strong>rice vinegar </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar </strong>and set aside<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>quick-pickled shallot</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1715617577098-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1715617577098-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
