    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>chicken thighs</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until lightly browned</p><p>Once browned, add your <strong>red Thai curry paste</strong> with a couple of splashes of <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> and cook, covered, for a further 10 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1715617586218-x200.jpg",
