    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Remove the tray with the fries from the oven and add the <strong>brioche halves</strong></p><p>Return the tray to the oven for a final 4-5 min or until the brioche is warmed through</p>",
