    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, transfer the chicken to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks - this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Return the <strong>pulled chicken</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>Thai-style chicken</strong></p>",
