    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble, add a little <strong>sriracha mayo </strong>to the <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>brioche base </strong>and top with the<strong> Thai-style chicken</strong>, <strong>crispy shallot</strong>, some <strong>quick-pickled Asian-style slaw </strong>and a <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>brioche lid</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>fries</strong>, <strong>remaining quick-pickled Asian-style slaw</strong> and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>sriracha mayo</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
